needsUpdate

public boolean needsUpdate()
Checks if the camera needs to be updated. More detailed information can be collected over isOutstandingForSubscription() and isOutstandingForUnsubscription() If and only if it returns true it is guaranteed, that exactly one out of isOutstandingForSubscription() and isOutstandingForUnsubscription() returns true.

Returns:
boolean returns true if the selection status differs from the subscription status

isOutstandingForSubscription

public boolean isOutstandingForSubscription()
Checks if this camera needs to be subscribed. If this returns true the method isOutstandingForUnsubscription() cannot return true.

Returns:
true if this cam is not subscribed yet but selected, false otherwise

isOutstandingForUnsubscription

public boolean isOutstandingForUnsubscription()
Checks if this camera needs to be unsubscribed. If this method return true, the method isOutstandingForSubscription() cannot return true

Returns:
true if this camera is subscribed but no more selected, false otherwise
